# apps/medusa's `medusa build` bundles its admin dashboard with Vite,
# which resolves each Medusa admin-extension package (@medusajs/dashboard,
# @medusajs/draft-order/admin, etc.) via plain Node resolution from
# apps/medusa's own node_modules — that only works if those packages
# are hoisted to a place Node's default (non-pnpm-symlink-aware)
# resolution can find, hence this narrow hoist pattern rather than a
# blanket `shamefully-hoist=true`. No other app in this monorepo
# depends on any @medusajs/* or react/react-dom package, so this has no
# effect on how they resolve their own dependencies.
public-hoist-pattern[]=@medusajs/*
public-hoist-pattern[]=react
public-hoist-pattern[]=react-dom
